│ The fix is to add a null check for `UnderlyingObject` before it is used in the `isa<AllocaInst>` call.                                                                                   │
│                                                                                                                                                                                          │
│ I will modify `llvm/lib/Transforms/IPO/FunctionAttrs.cpp` to add this check.                                                                                                             │
│                                                                                                                                                                                          │
